[28.346796, "o", "\u001b[?2004h> "]
[28.347735, "o", "Remove the string-matching rules and the explicit DROP rules for ports 80/443. If access control is needed, implement proper authentication at the application layer, use source IP whitelisting, or deploy a proper Web Application Firewall (WAF). Content-based filtering should be done at Layer 7 (application layer) not Layer 4 (transport layer).\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r"]
